Deployment of a Reactive Web Page Using Jenkins and Docker
🎯 Aim
To create and deploy a reactive web page using Jenkins running in Docker by using JavaScript for dynamic content updates.

✅ Step 1 — Open Docker Desktop


Open Docker Desktop


Wait until Docker is running



✅ Step 2 — Open Command Prompt


Press Win + R


Type cmd


Press Enter



✅ Step 3 — Create project folder
Copy and paste:
